Hershey Simplex font data
=========================

Neeh includes a converted subset of the Hershey Fonts from the futural.jhf
data distributed by the hershey-fonts project:

https://github.com/kamalmostafa/hershey-fonts

Required acknowledgements:

- The Hershey Fonts were created by Dr. A. V. Hershey while working at the
  United States National Bureau of Standards.
- The distribution format for the font data was created by James Hurt,
  Cognition, Inc., 900 Technology Park Drive, Billerica, MA 01821, USA.

The Hershey font data may be used for commercial and non-commercial purposes.
It must not be converted into the proprietary font-data format distributed by
the United States National Technical Information Service (NTIS).
